videos.description: SFA's Shannon Bogues shoots a deep 3-pointer which takes a couple bounces off the rim the luckily rolls in.
videos.headline: Bogues' deep 3 takes a lucky bounce

videos.description: TJ Holyfield takes the pass from Ivan Canete after setting a pick then proceeds to throw it down to extend the lead for the Lumberjacks.
videos.headline: Holyfield throws it down for SFA

videos.description: After SE Louisiana grabs an offensive rebound, Eddy Polanco drives then dishes it off to Moses Greenwood who sinks the layup giving the Lions the lead.
videos.headline: Lions take the lead after trailing by 14

videos.description: Marlain Veal drives past a group of SFA defenders and gets up high for the layup to keep SE Louisiana's hopes alive.
videos.headline: Veal gets up to keep the Lions in contention

videos.description: SFA grabs the offensive rebound after a missed Ivan Canete free throw and Canete puts it back to extend the Jackrabbits' late lead.
videos.headline: Canete's putback helps seal the win for SFA

videos.description: In a game that came down to the last few minutes, the Stephen F. Austin Lumberjacks edge out the SE Louisiana Lions to win the Southland conference championship.
videos.headline: SFA survives late push and wins conference championship title
